<%# Origin: https://github.com/projectblacklight/blacklight/blob/v7.37.0/app/views/kaminari/blacklight/_paginator.html.erb

Overrides Blacklight's Kaminari view partial _paginator.html.erb to move the "next" button to the end of the paginator.
This particular paginator is located at the bottom of the search results page (there are multiple different paginators).

The container tag
  - available local variables
    current_page:  a page object for the currently displayed page
    num_pages:     total number of pages
    per_page:      number of items to fetch per page
    remote:        data-remote
    paginator:     the paginator that renders the pagination tags inside

   Paginator now using the Bootstrap paginator class
-%>
<%= paginator.render do -%>
  <ul class="pagination">
    <%= prev_page_tag %>
    <% each_relevant_page do |page| -%>
      <% if page.left_outer? || page.right_outer? || page.inside_window? -%>
        <%= page_tag page %>
      <% elsif !page.was_truncated? -%>
        <%= gap_tag %>
      <% end -%>
    <% end -%>  
    <%= next_page_tag  %>
  </ul>
<% end -%>